<subSubSection id="FC8E653B874BB1111B005B66FBFBF26C" box="[89,1135,3444,3473]" pageId="4" pageNumber="197" type="activity">
<paragraph id="B42B36B0874BB1111B005B66FBFBF26C" blockId="4.[89,1294,2968,3473]" box="[89,1135,3444,3473]" pageId="4" pageNumber="197">
<emphasis id="86E0EAA2874BB1111B005B66FED7F26C" bold="true" box="[89,323,3444,3473]" pageId="4" pageNumber="197">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Nelson’s Spiny Pocket Mouse is nocturnal and terrestrial.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
