<subSubSection id="FC8E653B874BB1111E09577EF728FE21" pageId="4" pageNumber="197" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="B42B36B0874BB1111E09577EF728FE21" blockId="4.[1359,2566,285,557]" pageId="4" pageNumber="197">
<emphasis id="86E0EAA2874BB1111E09577EF927FE70" bold="true" box="[1360,1715,364,397]" pageId="4" pageNumber="197">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. Main conservation threat to Nelson’s Spiny Pocket Mouse is significant loss of habitat through logging and subsequent fragmentation, landslides, and floods.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
